{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/yarn-pnp","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"57836fb1-7b26-5e35-ad49-5b3a09f373e1","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/a40a7/yarn.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.13636363636363%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/8ac56/yarn.webp 240w,\n/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/d3be9/yarn.webp 480w,\n/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/e46b2/yarn.webp 960w,\n/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/f992d/yarn.webp 1440w,\n/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/882b9/yarn.webp 1920w,\n/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/491cb/yarn.webp 2200w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/09b79/yarn.jpg 240w,\n/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/7cc5e/yarn.jpg 480w,\n/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/6a068/yarn.jpg 960w,\n/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/644c5/yarn.jpg 1440w,\n/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/0f98f/yarn.jpg 1920w,\n/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/a40a7/yarn.jpg 2200w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/a364689085220ed90f6f39067fe01d6c/6a068/yarn.jpg\"\n          alt=\"yarn\"\n          title=\"yarn\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>2020年1月下旬，Node包管理工具Yarn推出了2.0版本。1.12版本开始加入的PnP功能默认包含。</p>\n<h2 id=\"历史\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8E%86%E5%8F%B2\" aria-label=\"历史 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>历史</h2>\n<p>随着前端领域的飞速发展，前端的库越来越多。为了更好地管理各种各样的库，Nodejs推出了官方的包管理工具npm。</p>\n<p>在npm5之前，npm cli使用体检不佳:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>没有依赖锁定使得不同环境安装可能会出现版本冲突；</li>\n<li>没有本地离线缓存功能，无网环境下会安装失败；</li>\n<li>依赖安装比较慢。</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p>npm5起加入了版本锁定等功能，提高了依赖安装速度。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>因为npm存在的这些问题，Yarn横空出世，给npm依赖的安装管理带来了便利的交互和更快的速度等。</p>\n<h2 id=\"yarn-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#yarn-2\" aria-label=\"yarn 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Yarn 2</h2>\n<p>因为<code class=\"language-text\">(感谢)</code>yarn的存在，npm改进了自身cli的体验，加入了版本锁定等提升安装速度的特性。现在日常使用中npm、yarn两者安装的速度已经相差无几。</p>\n<p>但是，node项目始终存在问题——依赖目录<code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>过重。占用过大、文件过多，安装过程中IO开销过大。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>一个同事的Windows电脑，磁盘速度不快。出现问题时删除项目的<code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>花费了10分钟(基本每次都是喝杯茶回来才好)。</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>目录太复杂，且文件又多又小，比较吃磁盘。</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<p>来自yarn官方对于node包解析低效的原因说明:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>目录通常包含了大量的文件，<code class=\"language-text\">yarn install</code>时可能会花超过70%的时间生成它们。由于包管理工具依然会将已存在的<code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>和期待结果进行diff，所以即便之前已经执行过install操作也无法挽救。</li>\n<li>因为<code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>的生成是IO密集操作，包管理工具除了做简单的文件拷贝(甚至在可能时，可以使用硬链接或者<code class=\"language-text\">copy-on-write</code>技术)之外没有其他办法更好的优化方法，仍需在操作磁盘的大量系统调用前diff文件差异。</li>\n<li>因为Node没有包的概念，它也不知道文件是否<code class=\"language-text\">应该</code>被访问(<code class=\"language-text\">与其相对的是被标记表示需要使用</code>)。完全可能出现这样的场景，因为忘记在<code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code>中列举了部分依赖导致开发环境可用的代码在生产环境出现问题。</li>\n<li>甚至在运行时，Node的解析机制需要大量的<code class=\"language-text\">stat</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">readdir</code>系统调用去计算每个被require的文件的路径位置。这是极其浪费的，也是Node应用启动耗时长的部分原因。</li>\n<li>最后，<code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>目录不支持包管理工具合理扁平处理包文件结构，这一设计是不切实际的。即使有些算法可以拿来优化依赖树的结构，但依旧不能优化一些特定的场景——不仅导致了文件磁盘占用比预期高，也使得一些包在内存中被实例化多次。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Ps</em> <code class=\"language-text\">versus being available by the sheer virtue of hoisting</code> => 不理解，就翻译成了<code class=\"language-text\">与其相对的是被标记表示需要使用</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>例1:\n以<code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code>为例，一行代码未写，已经占用了<code class=\"language-text\">188MB</code>。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 770px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b7cc7c92a61a49874930d1cbe749284a/e6e7b/create-react-app.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.22077922077922%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b7cc7c92a61a49874930d1cbe749284a/8ac56/create-react-app.webp 240w,\n/static/b7cc7c92a61a49874930d1cbe749284a/d3be9/create-react-app.webp 480w,\n/static/b7cc7c92a61a49874930d1cbe749284a/cf403/create-react-app.webp 770w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 770px) 100vw, 770px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/b7cc7c92a61a49874930d1cbe749284a/09b79/create-react-app.jpg 240w,\n/static/b7cc7c92a61a49874930d1cbe749284a/7cc5e/create-react-app.jpg 480w,\n/static/b7cc7c92a61a49874930d1cbe749284a/e6e7b/create-react-app.jpg 770w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 770px) 100vw, 770px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/b7cc7c92a61a49874930d1cbe749284a/e6e7b/create-react-app.jpg\"\n          alt=\"create react app\"\n          title=\"create react app\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>例2:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0008f169794a833b9714a5f519325134/a2510/node_modules.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/0008f169794a833b9714a5f519325134/8ac56/node_modules.webp 240w,\n/static/0008f169794a833b9714a5f519325134/d3be9/node_modules.webp 480w,\n/static/0008f169794a833b9714a5f519325134/e46b2/node_modules.webp 960w,\n/static/0008f169794a833b9714a5f519325134/a5d4d/node_modules.webp 1000w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/0008f169794a833b9714a5f519325134/09b79/node_modules.jpg 240w,\n/static/0008f169794a833b9714a5f519325134/7cc5e/node_modules.jpg 480w,\n/static/0008f169794a833b9714a5f519325134/6a068/node_modules.jpg 960w,\n/static/0008f169794a833b9714a5f519325134/a2510/node_modules.jpg 1000w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/0008f169794a833b9714a5f519325134/6a068/node_modules.jpg\"\n          alt=\"node modules\"\n          title=\"node modules\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>为了解决<code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>目录存在的问题，Yarn正式推出了Yarn 2，加入了pnp(<code class=\"language-text\">Plug&#39;n&#39;Play</code>)功能。</p>\n<h3 id=\"pnp\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#pnp\" aria-label=\"pnp permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>PnP</h3>\n<p>PnP，<code class=\"language-text\">Plug&#39;n&#39;Play</code>的缩写，意为即插即用。</p>\n<p>启用PnP后(Yarn 2默认启用)，<code class=\"language-text\">yarn install</code>不再生成<code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>目录，而是生成了<code class=\"language-text\">.yarn</code>目录和<code class=\"language-text\">.pnp.js</code>文件。</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">.yarn</code>目录存放了项目中下载的所有依赖的zip包，<code class=\"language-text\">.pnp.js</code>的内容是项目的npm模块解析规则。</p>\n<h4 id=\"使用\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用🌰</h4>\n<p>下面以本地安装并console.log<code class=\"language-text\">ramda</code>为例。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>新建项目，加入依赖<code class=\"language-text\">ramda</code></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"dependencies\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"ramda\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^0.27.0\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>yarn install</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/92987/yarn-install.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.215155615696887%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/8ac56/yarn-install.webp 240w,\n/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/d3be9/yarn-install.webp 480w,\n/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/e46b2/yarn-install.webp 960w,\n/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/f992d/yarn-install.webp 1440w,\n/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/9bf70/yarn-install.webp 1478w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/09b79/yarn-install.jpg 240w,\n/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/7cc5e/yarn-install.jpg 480w,\n/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/6a068/yarn-install.jpg 960w,\n/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/644c5/yarn-install.jpg 1440w,\n/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/92987/yarn-install.jpg 1478w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/485bbfaee9f6bddebf84bc020f0ebb67/6a068/yarn-install.jpg\"\n          alt=\"yarn install\"\n          title=\"yarn install\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 404px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/979170bd67d246cb1be33141eb0097c8/e75d0/yarn-install-folder.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 112.37623762376236%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/979170bd67d246cb1be33141eb0097c8/8ac56/yarn-install-folder.webp 240w,\n/static/979170bd67d246cb1be33141eb0097c8/3a65f/yarn-install-folder.webp 404w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 404px) 100vw, 404px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/979170bd67d246cb1be33141eb0097c8/09b79/yarn-install-folder.jpg 240w,\n/static/979170bd67d246cb1be33141eb0097c8/e75d0/yarn-install-folder.jpg 404w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 404px) 100vw, 404px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/979170bd67d246cb1be33141eb0097c8/e75d0/yarn-install-folder.jpg\"\n          alt=\"yarn install folder\"\n          title=\"yarn install folder\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>yarn run test</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在package.json中定义”test”</p>\n<p>“test” => “node -e ‘console.log(require(”ramda”))‘”</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 764px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7b83d600848e018522848d70484a41fa/72747/yarn-run-script.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.5392670157068%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7b83d600848e018522848d70484a41fa/8ac56/yarn-run-script.webp 240w,\n/static/7b83d600848e018522848d70484a41fa/d3be9/yarn-run-script.webp 480w,\n/static/7b83d600848e018522848d70484a41fa/79237/yarn-run-script.webp 764w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 764px) 100vw, 764px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7b83d600848e018522848d70484a41fa/09b79/yarn-run-script.jpg 240w,\n/static/7b83d600848e018522848d70484a41fa/7cc5e/yarn-run-script.jpg 480w,\n/static/7b83d600848e018522848d70484a41fa/72747/yarn-run-script.jpg 764w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 764px) 100vw, 764px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/7b83d600848e018522848d70484a41fa/72747/yarn-run-script.jpg\"\n          alt=\"yarn run script\"\n          title=\"yarn run script\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>不能直接使用<code class=\"language-text\">node xxx.js</code>，因为node依赖解析的目录<code class=\"language-text\">node_modules</code>没了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f18f87e84dd9c396e36ea97ce9bc8695/bb3bf/node-run-script.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.65371024734982%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f18f87e84dd9c396e36ea97ce9bc8695/8ac56/node-run-script.webp 240w,\n/static/f18f87e84dd9c396e36ea97ce9bc8695/d3be9/node-run-script.webp 480w,\n/static/f18f87e84dd9c396e36ea97ce9bc8695/e46b2/node-run-script.webp 960w,\n/static/f18f87e84dd9c396e36ea97ce9bc8695/cc785/node-run-script.webp 1132w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/f18f87e84dd9c396e36ea97ce9bc8695/09b79/node-run-script.jpg 240w,\n/static/f18f87e84dd9c396e36ea97ce9bc8695/7cc5e/node-run-script.jpg 480w,\n/static/f18f87e84dd9c396e36ea97ce9bc8695/6a068/node-run-script.jpg 960w,\n/static/f18f87e84dd9c396e36ea97ce9bc8695/bb3bf/node-run-script.jpg 1132w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/f18f87e84dd9c396e36ea97ce9bc8695/6a068/node-run-script.jpg\"\n          alt=\"node run script\"\n          title=\"node run script\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h4 id=\"其他说明\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-label=\"其他说明 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>其他说明</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>PnP的依赖变成了zip包，可以上传VCS。开发、编译环境的依赖包可以做到完全一致，也可以省去安装的时间。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/yarnpkg/berry\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">yarn官方仓库</a>就使用了这种方式管理依赖。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 628px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/90735e572640f56d9c6452a3ea8d4fb7/b4e32/yarn-berry-repo.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 95.54140127388536%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/90735e572640f56d9c6452a3ea8d4fb7/8ac56/yarn-berry-repo.webp 240w,\n/static/90735e572640f56d9c6452a3ea8d4fb7/d3be9/yarn-berry-repo.webp 480w,\n/static/90735e572640f56d9c6452a3ea8d4fb7/724e7/yarn-berry-repo.webp 628w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 628px) 100vw, 628px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/90735e572640f56d9c6452a3ea8d4fb7/09b79/yarn-berry-repo.jpg 240w,\n/static/90735e572640f56d9c6452a3ea8d4fb7/7cc5e/yarn-berry-repo.jpg 480w,\n/static/90735e572640f56d9c6452a3ea8d4fb7/b4e32/yarn-berry-repo.jpg 628w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 628px) 100vw, 628px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/90735e572640f56d9c6452a3ea8d4fb7/b4e32/yarn-berry-repo.jpg\"\n          alt=\"yarn berry repo\"\n          title=\"yarn berry repo\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n</li>\n<li>因为PnP、Yarn才刚推出不久，不推荐项目直接升级。</li>\n<li>\n<p>前端社区其他工具链支持度还不够，从官方看已有下列的工具有条件支持(某版本起或插件支持)。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>来自<a href=\"https://yarnpkg.com/features/pnp#caveats-and-work-in-progress\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">yarn官方站说明</a>。</p>\n<p>Babel</p>\n<p>Create-React-App</p>\n<p>ESLint</p>\n<p>Husky</p>\n<p>Jest</p>\n<p>Prettier</p>\n<p>Rollup</p>\n<p>TypeScript-ESLint</p>\n<p>WebStorm</p>\n<p>TypeScript</p>\n<p>VSCode-ESLint</p>\n<p>VSCode</p>\n<p>Webpack</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"总结\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93\" aria-label=\"总结 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>总结</h2>\n<p>yarn pnp的出现给前端工程角度带来了新的方向，值得尝试和探索。</p>\n<p>对个人开发者来说可能影响不大，但是团队、公司层面的项目需要慎重，可以尝鲜，不建议直接切换。</p>\n<p>总的来说，前端又有新玩具了😁。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83\" aria-label=\"参考 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>参考</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://yarnpkg.com/features/pnp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">yarn pnp介绍</a></li>\n</ol>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/yarn-pnp","tagSlugs":["/tag/yarn/","/tag/前端/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-02-15 15:30","description":"2020年1月下旬，Node包管理工具Yarn推出了2.0版本。1.12版本开始加入的PnP功能默认包含。","tags":["Yarn","前端"],"title":"Yarn PnP","socialImage":"yarn.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/yarn-pnp"}}}